--=== Experience ===--  (Guild Help)

The following are the amounts of experience necessary to obtain each level.
These are the amounts of spent experience, and are not cumulative.
Refer to help file on hm_exp for levels above 20.
Advancing a fourth guild is possible after obtaining at least levels 30/30/20.

